{"tid":2094644,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Hamilton》音樂劇Disney+上架","createTime":"2020-07-04T20:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T11:47:49.000Z","uid":115066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"384b64c961dd15850f6e585041512592191e9081","tid":2094644,"uid":115066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T20:19:46.000Z","msg":"2020年2月3日，華特迪士尼影業宣布以7500萬美元買下該音樂劇的現場錄像電影版本發行權，並宣布將於2021年10月15日在電影院上映。2020年5月12日，該劇作者米蘭達表示，由於2019冠狀病毒疫情導致百老匯暫停所有演出，電影將提檔至2020年7月4日獨立日當天，但改爲直接上綫迪士尼+。電影將採用與2016年在理察&middot;羅傑斯劇院演出時的錄像。<br />\n<br />\n作者Lin-Manuel Miranda，另一個成名作In the Heights 亦都改編造電影版，不過武肺關係廷遲到出年上映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa1f41d3ae4ae1d0542f5c6bab7e61d5d521d9e","tid":2094644,"uid":16567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T20:46:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾奶共迪迪尼<br />\n狗也不屌"},{"pid":"84aab097cd6af591437e05331772ca8333949bec","tid":2094644,"uid":115066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bde3e472b607ebfc7b7f939ceb89ed00bab76c","tid":2094644,"uid":115066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba959f8c92679f1487c75ebb4a265e36180ed47","tid":2094644,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"好好睇，近十年寫得最好嘅音樂劇，美國hit爆，但同其他國家文化差異實在太大"},{"pid":"438aa6c8b2d98d4159d55636b0ea2a9e1d1928ea","tid":2094644,"uid":115066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ba959f8c92679f1487c75ebb4a265e36180ed47","tid":2094644,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"好好睇，近十年寫得最好嘅音樂劇，美國hit爆，但同其他國家文化差異實在太大"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"美國歷史+hip hop +音樂劇，叫人睇係有D難度。不過實在太神級，已經同其他百老滙經典睇齊，再出電影版都係